      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">The Exchange Decision</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300">Exchanging tiles costs you a turn — roughly 25-30 points of expected value. But sometimes it's the best play:</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-green-500/30 bg-green-950/10">
          <p class="text-green-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✓ Exchange When</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Best play scores under 10 points. Bag has 7+ tiles remaining. You're not more than 60 points behind. Your rack has no S, blank, or power tile worth keeping.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 rounded-xl border border-red-500/30 bg-red-950/10">
          <p class="text-red-400 font-semibold text-sm mb-1">✗ Don't Exchange When</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Bag has fewer than 7 tiles. You're significantly behind (need points now). You can score 15+ even with a bad rack. The endgame is approaching.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-4 rounded-xl border border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-950/10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-6 text-center">
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">25-30</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Expected point cost of exchanging</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">4-6</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Optimal tiles to exchange</p></div>
          <div><p class="text-xl font-bold text-amber-400">7+</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-400">Minimum bag tiles needed</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-light text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 mt-10 mb-4 border-l-4 border-amber-400 pl-4">Psychology: Staying Calm</h2>

      <p class="text-gray-300">Bad tiles trigger tilt. Tilt causes rushed decisions. Rushed decisions compound the damage. Break the cycle:</p>

      <div class="not-prose my-6 p-5 rounded-xl border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-950/10">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">🧩 Mental Reset Process</p>
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">1</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Acknowledge the bad draw without emotion. It's random variance, not personal.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple-900/50 border border-purple-500/40 flex items-center justify-center text-xs text-purple-300 font-bold">2</span>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-300">Shift your goal: instead of "score big", think "minimise damage and improve my leave".</p>
          </div>
